London Data Store scraping script.
Returns tab delimited list of datasets available ~ URL\tTitle\tCategory

$ ./londondatastoredatasets.pl

http://london.data.gov.uk/datastore/package/active-people-survey-competition	Active People Survey - Competition	Sport
http://london.data.gov.uk/datastore/package/active-people-survey-participation	Active People Survey - Participation	Sport
http://london.data.gov.uk/datastore/package/active-people-survey-satisfaction	Active People Survey - Satisfaction	Sport
http://london.data.gov.uk/datastore/package/active-people-survey-tuition	Active People Survey - Tuition	Sport
http://london.data.gov.uk/datastore/package/active-people-survey-volunteering	Active People Survey - Volunteering	Sport


